To install kaggle datasets we must download it from the terminal
    pip install kaggle

Update pip
    python.exe -m pip install --upgrade pip

Download API Key from creating Kaggle account, found within settings and create API [https://www.kaggle.com/account/login?phase=startRegisterTab&returnUrl=%2Fcreate-account]
toke, it will download a .json file named 'kaggle.json', place it in a '.kaggle' directory
*MUST BE IN C:\Users\{PC_USER}\*
NOTES FOR COMMANDS
ls -> list (lists files in that directory
cd -> change directories
EX. cd ../ (../ is to go back)

Real life example:
 C:\Users\{PC_USER}\[project_name]
 cd ../
 C:\Users\{PC_USER}
 mkdir .kaggle

Copy file from the download path folder (Find .json and right click and copy PATH)
    cp C:\Users\{PC_USER}\Downloads\kaggle.json

To find datasets list
    kaggle datasets list -s '{DESIRED_DATASET}'
Ex.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
mlg-ulb/creditcardfraud                                           Credit Card Fraud Detection                        66MB  2018-03-23 01:17:27
655870(DownloadCount)         11083(VoteCounts)     0.85294116(Usability)
whenamancodes/fraud-detection                                     Fraud Detection                                    66MB  2022-09-12 11:54:40
6990(DownloadCount)           97(VoteCounts)     1.0(Usability)
ealaxi/paysim1                                                    Synthetic Financial Datasets For Fraud Detection  178MB  2017-04-03 08:40:34
86276(DownloadCount)          1330(VoteCounts)     0.88235295(Usability)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

To download dataset list .zip file
     kaggle datasets download -d 'mlg-ulb/creditcardfraud'

Go to downloaded file *in file explorer* and extract in
    C:\Users\gianc\PycharmProjects\Hate-Speech-Detection

Then rename folder to data for readability